Package: lmd
Depends: lmd-server, lmd-manager-cli, lmd-lliurex-data
Architecture: all
Description: LMD Metapackage
 This package contains all dependencies to prepare 
 an LTPS/LMD server.

Package: lmd-server
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dnsmasq, ltsp, ltsp-binaries, php-cli, apache2, libapache2-mod-php7.4, llx-netinstall , n4d-lliurex-base , llx-bootmanager , util-linux, python3-apt, n4d-taskscheduler-server, n4d-taskscheduler-client, python3-sh, isomaker, lliurex-maker, n4d-locale-manager
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP Management for Dummies.
 This package gives support to Thin and Fat
 Thin Clients Management.

Package: lmd-manager-cli
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP Management for Dummies. Cli tools.
 LMD gives support to Thin and Fat
 Thin Clients Management. This package
 offers CLI tools to manage LMD.

Package: lmd-lliurex-data
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, lmd-server
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP links and data for LliureX.
 This package contains all cool data, links
 and templates to working with LMD in LliureX.

Package: admin-center-ltsp
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, admin-center
Architecture: all
Description: LMD - LTSP Module for admin-center.
 LTSP gives support to Thin and Fat
 Thin Clients Management. This package
 offers a module for Admin Center to
 manage LTSP.

Package: vnc-disable-composite
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Architecture: all
Description: Plasma disabler composite during vnc session.
 Xdg autostart script that disables composition 
 on vnc sessions invoking dbus method.


